Hi Andrey,

Over the past decade, first through our own angel investing and then
through MyAsiaVC, we kept seeing the same pattern: exceptional technical
Asian founders building AI businesses that are global from day one, whether
from Asia or through the US diaspora.

Contra VC was built around that opportunity. We=E2=80=99re now raising Fund=
 I, a 30M
Pre-Seed and Seed fund focused on AI & Robotics, pairing early conviction
with cross-border operator support across Asia and the US.

Through MyAsiaVC as an investment platform, we have deployed 70M+ across
260+ investments and built a 5,800+ LP community. LPs in the fund also
receive priority access to co-invest via SPVs.

Would you be open to a short conversation to exchange views on where the
next wave of AI companies is emerging? Happy to send a brief overview ahead
of time.

Best regards,
